# Advantages of MCP Clients

- Dynamic tool discovery
- No hardcoded tool definitions
- Connect to multiple MCP servers
- Reusable tool ecosystem
- Easier maintenance
- Better scalability
- Standardized communication
- Works with local and remote servers

---

# Multiple Server Support

One MCP client can connect to multiple servers simultaneously.

```
             MCP Client
          ┌──────┼──────┐
          │      │      │
          ▼      ▼      ▼
      Weather  GitHub  Database
       Server   Server   Server
```

This allows a single LangGraph agent to access tools from different domains. :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}

